song.title: Tekilla Groove II
song.info:
NEWS: I’m thrilled to let you know that the chiptune EP “Zalza vs. the World Vol. 1″ is to be released worldwide on September 28! The chiptune compilation Zalza vs. the World will be released in three volumes – Containing vs. tracks with chip-heroes like Xylo & Cerror, Wiklund, Beek, Floppi, Joule, Michu, josSs, Dalezy amongst others!
Follow me so you don't miss it! --
Tekilla Groove II, track featured on the the chipalbum Back to the chipland (BTTC). Released 2010-06-10.
